remarks.example:
The following example shows how to create/modify a GL account:

            GL.Account glacc = GL.Account._FindObjectByCode(dcCode);
            if (glacc == null)
            {
                glacc = new GL.Account();
                glacc.Code = dcCode;
            }
            glacc.Description = "SDK Test Sales Account";
            glacc.Type = EvolutionSdk.GL.AccountType.TradingIncome;
            glacc.Save();
